CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, National Edition, August 15, 1942, pg. 9, reads: "As in former years, Frog Week in Pittsburgh was gay and exciting, and complete with varied activities.  Photographer Harris has recorded some of the scenes for our readers.  Top row: Pretty Louise Johnson, left, and Shirley Washington with Lt. Henry B. Favers having a hearty laugh..."
TitMainTitle: Lt. Henry B. Favers wearing military uniform, standing between Shirley Louise Johnson and Shirley Washington, posed outdoors in front of picnic table during FROGS week activities, possibly South Park
